rs a tested and robust API, and is freely\navailable under the BSD license at github.com/ged-lab/khmer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Sep 2013 21:08:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2013 20:15:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 May 2014 03:58:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 14 Jul 2014 17:05:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-07"}
